quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  53,26,Zingaphi iingelosi ezisezulwini ezintethelelo yazo ingayi kunceda nto ngaphandle kokuba uAllâh Ade Anike imvume kulowo Athande ukumnika namamkeleyo
  53,27,Inene abo bangakholwayo kuBomi oBuzayo bathiya iingelosi amagama esikhomokazi
  53,28,"Yaye malunga noko abanalwazi, akukho nto balandela yona ngaphandle koqash qash, inene, uqash-qash akancedi nto ngokuchasene nenyaniso"
  53,29,Wena zikhwebule kulowo utshikilela umyalezo weThu ongafuni nto ngaphandle kobomi beli hlabathi
  53,30,"Lowo ngumyinge wolwazi lwabo, inene iNkosi yakho yiYona, Yaziyo okokuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, ikwayiYo kananjalo Eyaziyo ukuba ngubani na okuso isiKhokelo"
  53,31,"Kananjalo kokuka-Allah okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni khon’ukuze Abuyekeze abo benza ukungcola (ngesohlwayo) ngoko bakwenzayo, Abuyekeze nabo benza okulungileyo (ngomvuzo) omhle"
  53,32,"Abo baziphephayo izono ezikhulu nezenzo ezingcolileyo, benze ezincinane kuphela, inene iNkosi yenu Iphangalele kuxolelo (lwezono), Yona Inazi kakuhle xa Inivelisa4 emhlabeni naxa naniizintsana ezibelekweni zoomama benu. Ngoko ke musani ukubanga ukuba ninyulu, Yena nguYena Waziyo ukuba ngubani na oMoyikayo"
  53,33,"Umbonile na lowo utshikileyo wafulathela, (i-Islam)"
  53,34,Waza wanikela kancinane waphinda wayeka
  53,35,"Ingaba unalo na ulwazi lokungabonwayo, ukuze abone"
  53,36,Akachazelwanga na ngokwakuseziBhalweni zikaMûsâ
  53,37,"NezikaIbrahim, owazalisekisayo"
  53,38,Akukho mthwali wamithwalo uya kuthwaliswa umthwalo womnye
  53,39,Kananjalo akukho nto umntu (aya kuyifumana) ngaphandle kwaleyo wayizabalazelayo
  53,40,Kwaye inene umzamo wakhe uza kubonwa
  53,41,Aze abuyekezwe ngawo ngembuyekezo egcweleyo
  53,42,Kananjalo eNkosini yakho kulapho isiphelo sikhoyo
  53,43,Inene yiYo (iNkosi yakho) Eyenza umntu ahleke aphinde alile
  53,44,IkwayiYo Eyenza ukufa Inike ubomi
  53,45,IkwayiYo Edala abalingane oyindoda nowasetyhini
  53,46,Ngeqabaza lembewu yomntu xa likhutshiwe
  53,47,Kuze (kube yimfuneko) kuYe (ukuba Adale) enye indalo
  53,48,NguYe kananjalo Otyebisayo5 Anelise
  53,49,Kananjalo nguYe iNkosi kaSirius
  53,50,Ukanti Yena Watshabalalisa abantu bokuqala bakwa’Ad
  53,51,NabakwaThamûd nabo Akazanga Abasindise
  53,52,Nabantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili. Inene yayingabo abaya ababi nabulungisa baba ngabacinezeli
  53,53,"Ke\tkaloku\tWazitshabalalisa\tizixeko\tezabhedululwayo Wazikhahlela phantsi"
  53,54,Wabagqumelela ngoko Wabagqumelela ngako
  53,55,ZiziphinakeezintsikelelozeNkosiyenuniyakuzithandabuza
  53,56,"Lo\t(Mprofeti)\tnguMlumkisi\tnjengabanye\tabaLumkisi bamandulo"
  53,57,IMini esondelayo isondele (yona)
  53,58,"Mayela\tnayo\takukho\tbani\tngaphandle\tkoAllâh Onokuyishenxisa"
  53,59,Ingaba le ntetho iyanimangalisa kusini na
  53,60,Ke kaloku nina niyahleka anilili
  53,61,Nibe nisadlalisa ngokuzonwabisa
  53,62,Qubudani ke nina (maMuslim) kuAllâh niMnqule. (Yena Yedwa)
  54,1,IYure sele ifikile yaye nenyanga sele icandeke (kubini)
  54,2,"Ke kaloku xa bebona umqondiso (ummangaliso), bayatshikila bathi: “(Lo) ngumlingo ogqithayo.”"
  54,3,"Kananjalo baye baphika, balandela iminqweno yabo. Kodwa into nganye inexesha lokufezekiswa (kwayo)"
  54,4,Ke kaloku sele ifikile kubo inkcazelo ekukho kuyo isilumkiso (esaneleyo ngokubhekiselele kugabadelo)
  54,5,Ubulumko obuphangaleleyo kodwa isilumkiso asibancedi (nto)
  54,6,"Bayeke ke (Muhammad), ngeMini uMkhwazi aya kubizela abantu kwinto engathandekiyo (uMlilo wesiHogo)"
  54,7,"Amehlo abo aya kuba ethobekile, baya kuphuma emangcwabeni wabo bengathi ziinkumbi bethe saa"
  54,8,"Begxalathelana besiya phambili kuMkhwazi. Abangakholwayo baya kuthi: “Le yiMini enzima.”"